    "longBusinessSummary": "Coma 18 Joint stock Company engages in the construction and real estate trading business in Vietnam. The company is involved in the activity of land use rights owned by the owner, user, or leased; construction of other civil technical works; construction and installation of urban, industrial, civil, transportation, irrigation, and port infrastructure; architectural infrastructure of industrial zones, urban areas, power line projects, and transformer stations. It also constructs bridges, ports, dikes, and culverts; constructs, supervises, and completes civil and industrial projects; invests in industrial parks; and undertakes hydropower plants, as well as provides investment consulting, management, and implementation of construction; waste treatment; fruit processing and preservation; and business development of housing and urban technical infrastructure. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam. Coma 18 Joint stock Company is a subsidiary of Construction Machinery Corporation-JSC.",
